{"id": 61074, "date": "2025-10-07T04:00:54", "date_gmt": "2025-10-07T11:00:54", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=61074"}, "modified": "2026-06-11T13:02:15", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-11T20:02:15", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-october-7-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/10/07/kingdom-of-days-october-7-2/", "title": {"rendered": "October 7"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1967:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles take part in a battle of the bands at the Middletown Community Center.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4741\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1967-1007/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1967-1007.jpg?fit=249%2C159&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"249,159\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1967-1007\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1967-1007.jpg?fit=249%2C159&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4741 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1967-1007.jpg?resize=249%2C159&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"249\" height=\"159\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1980:\u00a0</strong>At Night Two in Richfield on the River Tour, Bruce and the E Street Band play &#8220;You Can Look (But You Better Not Touch)&#8221; for the very first time.</p>\n<div id=\"v-43CW31ld-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/43CW31ld?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a guest appearance with Cats on a Smooth Surface at The Stone Pony in Asbury Park for a cover-filled set, including &#8220;Lucille,&#8221; &#8220;Little Latin Lupe Lu,&#8221; and more.</p>\n<div id=\"v-Od5POU9j-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Od5POU9j?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays in Africa for the very first time at the Human Rights Now! show at Zimbabwe&#8217;s National Sports Stadium in Harare, before a largely white South African audience. Watch Bruce&#8217;s recollection of the show below.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dY4IpKtNSJk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PSonVspGunA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21668\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1988-10-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?fit=2428%2C862&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2428,862\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1601138110&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1988-10-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?fit=758%2C269&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21668 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?resize=758%2C269&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"269\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?w=2428&amp;ssl=1 2428w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?resize=300%2C107&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?resize=1024%2C364&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?resize=768%2C273&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?resize=1536%2C545&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?resize=2048%2C727&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-10-07.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band close out the first leg of the Rising Tour at HSBC Arena in Buffalo, tour premiering &#8220;You Can Look (But You Better Not Touch),&#8221; &#8220;Tougher Than the Rest,&#8221; and &#8220;Lost in the Flood.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lTcTDFeyL78?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29915\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2002-10-07-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2002-10-07.jpg?fit=334%2C1859&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"334,1859\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1601138283&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2002-10-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2002-10-07.jpg?fit=184%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29915 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2002-10-07.jpg?resize=334%2C1859&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"334\" height=\"1859\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2002-10-07.jpg?w=334&amp;ssl=1 334w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2002-10-07.jpg?resize=54%2C300&amp;ssl=1 54w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2002-10-07.jpg?resize=184%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 184w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2002-10-07.jpg?resize=276%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 276w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 334px) 100vw, 334px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2005:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays a stellar acoustic set at the Hartford Civic Center, opening with &#8220;Back in Your Arms&#8221; and &#8220;Wreck on the Highway&#8221; and tour premiering &#8220;Something in the Night&#8221; and &#8220;You Can Look (But You Better Not Touch).&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hpPVKSv2m7M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21670\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2005-10-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2005-10-07.jpg?fit=1755%2C1640&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1755,1640\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1601138473&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2005-10-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2005-10-07.jpg?fit=758%2C708&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21670 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2005-10-07.jpg?resize=758%2C708&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"708\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2005-10-07.jpg?w=1755&amp;ssl=1 1755w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2005-10-07.jpg?resize=300%2C280&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2005-10-07.jpg?resize=1024%2C957&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2005-10-07.jpg?resize=768%2C718&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2005-10-07.jpg?resize=1536%2C1435&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2006:\u00a0</strong>Bruce&#8217;s tour of Italy continues as the Sessions Band arrives in Perugia and tour premieres &#8220;Factory&#8221; at Arena Santa Giuliana.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-uie0T55R3E?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oqe2DR_v8HQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9eg_lEC62cw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mYeiOaOluqU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WYJY0cxI0KA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>Bruce is interviewed by\u00a0<em>The New Yorker</em> editor David Remnick and reads from his book at Town Hall in New York City as part of The New Yorker Festival.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/i1PptJNEqIY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2017:\u00a0</strong>Bruce tweaks his\u00a0<em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>running order, swapping the positions of &#8220;Long Walk Home&#8221; and &#8220;The Rising.&#8221;</p>\n<p><strong>2020:\u00a0</strong>E Street Radio airs Volume 13 of Bruce&#8217;s\u00a0<em>From My Home to Yours</em> radio show, entitled &#8220;My Kingdom for a Car.&#8221;</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-61074-8\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2020-10-07-Bruce-E-Street-Radio-DJ-set-13-1.mp3?_=8\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2020-10-07-Bruce-E-Street-Radio-DJ-set-13-1.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2020-10-07-Bruce-E-Street-Radio-DJ-set-13-1.mp3</a></audio>\n<p>Later that day, Bruce records a promotional interview for\u00a0<em>Letter to You</em> with Zane Lowe. The interview will be aired on Apple Music later this month.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PhkL4K7Esc0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce debuted (and re-debuted, and re-debuted) &#8220;You Can Look (But You Better Not Touch)&#8221; on this date. Plus: Bruce recalls his first-ever show in Africa, is interviewed on-stage at The New Yorker Festival, and more.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 13348, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_feature_clip_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships